ue}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"蘭若鏑","primary":false}}]}},"person_2199316_translations":{"at":1772647195644,"data":{"id":2199316,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Titus Jin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"金弦，出生于北京。蒙古族、满族、回族、维吾尔族混血。精通中、英、法、德、西班牙语多种语言；精通小提琴和钢琴；精通绘画。2016年又开始练习跆拳道。 曾用圈名：妖精の飞羽、蓝逸、左边向北等。 经历 2007年5月，加入剪刀广播剧团。 2008年，毕业于多伦多大学。 2013年，在5sing创建了账号。 2016年，发行首张个人原创专辑《弦外之音》 2017年，加入729声工场。","name":"金弦","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"金弦","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Цзинь Сянь","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Titus Jin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"金弦","primary":false}}]}},"person_1173203_translations":{"at":1772647211784,"data":{"id":1173203,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Austin Wai Tin-chi (13 August 1957 – 4 October 2012) was a Hong Kong actor and choreographer. He was the elder brother of actress Kara Wai. He had notable roles in the martial arts films like The 36th Chamber of Shaolin, 5 Superfighters, The Avenging Eagle and Flash Point.","name":"Austin Wai Tin-Chi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"惠天赐籍贯山东，为满洲正黄旗后裔，因为在家中排行第四，所以在圈中有“小四”之名。惠天赐小时候曾经跟名旦粉菊花学京剧，10多岁加入邵氏拍电影，1978年以《枪神》崭露头角，1982年主演《帮规》和《英雄无泪》等电影。他在上世纪80年代加盟无线，先后参演83版《射雕英雄传》、《楚留香之蝙蝠传奇》等剧，其中以在《陆小凤之凤舞九天》中饰演的“剑神”西门吹雪一角最为经典。上世纪90年代他转投亚视，参与拍摄了《新包青天》、《傅红雪传奇》等剧。惠天赐近年淡出娱乐圈从商，偶尔客串电影如《星月童话》、《杀破狼》、《导火线》、《金钱帝国》等。这么多年来，他拍摄了超过70部电影。\n\n气宇轩昂的惠天赐情路十分坎坷，他在上世纪80年代与亚视前高层陈贝蒂结婚，二人育有两女惠颂玲及惠铠玲，却因为性格不合而离婚。大女儿的抚养权归陈贝蒂所有，小女儿虽然归他，但多由姑姑惠英红和奶奶管教。1996年，惠天赐与拍拖两年的女星斑斑结婚，二人育有一子，可惜最终还是在2001年离婚。","name":"惠天赐","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"惠天賜","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"혜천사","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"惠天賜，香港男演員，生於山東，據稱為滿洲正黃旗葉赫那拉氏後裔，祖上曾是富家子弟，至今山東老家還有個惠家莊園。他在家中排行老四，是女演員及香港金像影後惠英紅之胞兄。","name":"惠天賜","primary":false}}]}},"tv_314019_credits":{"at":1772647213326,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1516593,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Lang Yueting","original_name":"郎月婷","popularity":1.0816,"profile_path":"/bdyJhQrIG7ai9B2Tp2kD2M0F32X.jpg","character":"Ye Xi","credit_id":"6991291319bc3cd2ec6f64d6","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1613349,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Zhang Tianyang","original_name":"張天陽","popularity":1.2306,"profile_path":"/aT9PZ3TXTrstYB4iw7lxfhe7PWT.jpg","character":"Chen Guyuan","credit_id":"6991291b76fc6c7ae26f6368","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2582110,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Li Qing","original_name":"Li Qing","popularity":0.7314,"profile_path":"/22dSXLPk73d5saYkORamEEW6Z5b.jpg","character":"Chi Cheng","credit_id":"6991292cbdbfad0da1958b13","order":2},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1467182,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Wang Fang","original_name":"Wang Fang","popularity":0.248,"profile_path":"/hBCnqIMbZKmDVVR9piK7n1cPl1M.jpg","character":"Kang Zhao","credit_id":"69912937621a298bba84fe21","order":3},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":122818,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Lawrence Ng Kai-Wah","original_name":"吳啟華","popularity":1.6049,"profile_pat